==製作過程==
「沙家酒館」於2011年9月30日由TBS電視台預定製作[[電視試播|試播集]]。[[Steve_Byrne|Steve Byrne]]與[[Rob_Long|Rob Long]]編寫試播集，並由Byrne主演。<ref name="dl1">{{cite news |title=TBS Orders Pilot Starring Comedian Steve Byrne And Produced By Vince Vaughn |url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/09/tbs-orders-pilot-starring-comedian-steve-byrne-and-produced-by-vince-vaughn/ |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |date=2011-09-30 |first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |accessdate=2012-02-11 |archive-date=2012-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120112041340/http://www.deadline.com/2011/09/tbs-orders-pilot-starring-comedian-steve-byrne-and-produced-by-vince-vaughn/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在十月的時候，增加[[Valerie_Azlynn|Valerie Azlynn]]、[[Jodi_Long|Jodi Long]]、[[Vivian_Bang|Vivian Bang]]、[[Owen_Benjamin|Owen Benjamin]]與[[Dan_Lauria|Dan Lauria]]至劇組。本劇是在現場觀眾面前錄製。<ref name="dl2">{{cite news |title=Quartet Cast In TBS Comedy Pilot 'Sullivan And Son' Produced By Vince Vaughn |url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/10/quartet-cast-in-tbs-comedy-pilot-sullivan-and-son-produced-by-vince-vaughn/ |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |date=2011-10-24 |first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |accessdate=2012-02-11 |archive-date=2012-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120105194139/http://www.deadline.com/2011/10/quartet-cast-in-tbs-comedy-pilot-sullivan-and-son-produced-by-vince-vaughn/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="dl3">{{cite news |title=Cable Pilot Castings: Dan Lauria To Star In ‘Sullivan & Son’, Austin Butler In 'Intercept' |url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/10/cable-pilot-castings-dan-lauria-to-star-in-sullivan-son-austin-butler-in-intercept/ |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |date=2011-10-24 |first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |accessdate=2012-02-11 |archive-date=2012-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120105225445/http://www.deadline.com/2011/10/cable-pilot-castings-dan-lauria-to-star-in-sullivan-son-austin-butler-in-intercept/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

TBS電視台製播本劇是由於要跟[[TBBT|宅男行不行]]對打。<ref name="ppg">{{cite news |title=TBS grabs 'Sullivan and Son,' a fun portrait of Pittsburgh |url=http://www.post-gazette.com/pg/12041/1209378-67.stm |work=[[Pittsburgh_Post-Gazette|Pittsburgh Post-Gazette]] |date=2012-02-10 |first=Rob |last=Owen |accessdate=2012-02-11 |archive-date=2012-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120213005655/http://www.post-gazette.com/pg/12041/1209378-67.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在2012年前一齣劇[[Men_at_Work_(TV_series)|Men at Work]]收視不佳之後，TBS選擇本劇做為新的系列播出。<ref name="dl4">{{cite news |title=TBS Picks Up 'Sullivan And Son' To Series |url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/02/tbs-picks-up-sullivan-and-son-to-series/ |publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |date=2012-02-10 |first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |accessdate=2012-02-11 |archive-date=2012-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120211140302/http://www.deadline.com/2012/02/tbs-picks-up-sullivan-and-son-to-series/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在2012年2月10日，TBS電視台預定本劇十集並決定在2012年夏季播出。<ref name="ew">{{cite news |title=TBS greenlights Vince Vaughn-produced comedy starring Steve Byrne |url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2012/02/10/sullivan-son-steve-byrne-vince-vaughn/ |work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2012-02-10 |first=Mandi |last=Bierly |accessdate=2012-02-11 |archive-date=2012-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120213230355/http://insidetv.ew.com/2012/02/10/sullivan-son-steve-byrne-vince-vaughn/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=TBS Orders Vince Vaughn-Steve Byrne Comedy to Series |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/tbs-vince-vaughn-steve-byrne-sullivan-and-son-289297 |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2012-02-10 |first=Lesley |last=Goldberg |accessdate=2012-02-11 |archive-date=2012-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120213034154/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/tbs-vince-vaughn-steve-byrne-sullivan-and-son-289297 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在2012年秋季，TBS電視台宣布續訂第二季十集，並於2013年6月13日首播。<ref name="Renewal"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/sullivan-son-premiere-date-june-13-tbs/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-08-18 |archive-date=2013-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103072238/http://www.deadline.com/2013/04/sullivan-son-premiere-date-june-13-tbs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Renewal">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2012/09/04/tbs-orders-a-second-round-of-sullivan-son/147284/?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+Tvbythenumbers+%28TVbytheNumbers%29|title='Sullivan & Son' Renewed by TBS|date=September 4, 2012|last=Bibel|first=Sara|publisher=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]]|accessdate=September 4, 2012}}{{Dead link}}</ref>2013年8月20日，TBS宣布續訂本劇第三季共13集，大約於2014年中播出。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2013/08/20/sullivan-and-son-men-at-work-deal-with-it-renewed-by-tbs/198615|title='Sullivan and Son', 'Men At Work' & 'Deal With It' Renewed by TBS|last=Kondolojy|first=Amanda|work=TV by the Numbers|date=August 20, 2013|accessdate=2013-11-01|archive-date=2013-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131028082939/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2013/08/20/sullivan-and-son-men-at-work-deal-with-it-renewed-by-tbs/198615/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

